{
  "info": {
    "name": "MoviCore — Full API Collection",
    "description": "Colección completa para MoviCore. Cubre las 25 tablas de dominio del proyecto.\n\n## Setup\n1. Crear variable de entorno `base_url` en Postman con la URL del servidor (ej: `https://tanqueno-produccion.uaeftt-ute.site`)\n2. Ejecutar Login (admin) → el token se auto-asigna\n3. Para writes se necesita usuario administrador\n\n## Cobertura de tablas\n✅ 21/25 con endpoint directo\n✅ 4 indirectas: accounts_audit_log (signals), accounts_user_groups + accounts_user_user_permissions (admin), notifications_user_preference (auto-create)\n⏭️ 7 Django internas sin API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://tanqueno-produccion.uaeftt-ute.site", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "route_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "vehicle_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "trip_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driver_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "schedule_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "incident_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "incident_type_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "bus_stop_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
